## Inputs

- The diff is at HEAD~1..HEAD; use `git show HEAD` or `git diff
  HEAD~1 HEAD` to see it.
- The PRD is at `PRD.md`. ¬ß8 contains the architectural invariants
  you must enforce.
- The lessons file is at `lessons-learned.md`. Treat ¬ß1 as a list
